      the Service for personal, non-commercial use on devices you own or
      control. Each Pro license key may be activated on up to three devices at
      a time; you can deactivate a device from the popup and reuse the slot.
    </p>

    <h2>What you may not do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Reverse-engineer, decompile, or attempt to extract the source of the extension beyond what is exposed in the Chrome Web Store package itself.</li>
      <li>Share your license key publicly or with people who haven't paid for it.</li>
      <li>Use the Service to violate the terms of any third-party platform you watch video on (YouTube, Netflix, etc.). You are responsible for your own compliance with those platforms' terms.</li>
      <li>Resell, sublicense, or rebrand Subbun without our written permission.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-party platforms</h2>
    <p>
      Subbun is an independent product. We are not affiliated with, endorsed
      by, or sponsored by YouTube, Netflix, Amazon, Abema, Niconico,
      Crunchyroll, TVer, NHK, U-NEXT, Disney+, Hulu, or any other streaming
      service. We translate subtitles those services already provide. Site
      compatibility may break temporarily when these services update their
      players; we ship patches as quickly as we can.
    </p>

    <h2>Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
    <p>
      The Service is provided "as is" and "as available," without warranties
      of any kind. Translation quality is not guaranteed to be accurate for
      any specific purpose. Do not use Subbun for medical, legal, financial,
      or other critical decisions without independent verification.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      To the maximum extent permitted by law, Subbun and its operators are
      not liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or
      punitive damages, or for any loss of profits or revenues. Our total
      aggregate liability is limited to the amount you paid us in the 12
      months preceding the claim.
    </p>

    <h2>Termination</h2>
    <p>
      You may stop using the Service and uninstall the extension at any time.
      We may suspend or terminate your access (with refund of any prepaid
      unused portion, where applicable) if you materially breach these terms.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
